<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219431>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3 – 12. Superodontella tayaensi sp. nov.: 3, left antennal segments III and IV, dorsally; 4, left antennal segments III and IV, ventrally; 5, central area of head between d 1 and d 5 chaetae; 6, labial and perilabial chaetotaxy; 7, postantennal organ and ocelli; 8, maxilla and mandible; 9, dens and mucro; 10, distal part of leg I; 11, distal part of leg III." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219431/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219432>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12 – 14. Superodontella tayaensis sp. nov.: 12, anal valves chaetotaxy; 13, abdominal terga V and VI; 14, anal spines." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219432/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219430>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 2. Superodontella tayaensi sp. nov.: 1, habitus and dorsal chaetotaxy, s = s-chaeta; ms = microsensillum; 2, habitus and ventral chaetotaxy." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219430/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

